Name: Average time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time between SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and SW-Checklist Completed across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes for SW-Checklist Completed to occur after SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Total duration of the interval starting at SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and ending at SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Average time between SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and the subsequent activity in each variant path
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in variants where both activities occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to Plagiarism Originality Report Completed when the latter precedes the former in a case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Cycle time of the segment beginning with SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and ending with SW-Checklist Completed, compared to the cycle time of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average waiting time between SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and the next non-system-generated reminder or deadline-related activity (e.g., SW-Checklist Completion now due)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion now due'

Name: Total time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to SW-EIC Reject in variants that end with rejection without checklist completion
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and Manuscript Export Succeeded in cases where export occurs after the deadline notification
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Time elapsed from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to the first occurrence of any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection) in variants that proceed beyond AE assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Average duration between SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days and SW-Initial Reviewer Selection, highlighting delays introduced by pending checklist completion
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Total resolution time from SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days to final decision (e.g., SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Reject) in variants that include this activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'
